query:
SELECT TRIM(LEADING '0' FROM TRIM(civilId)) as normCid, 
  COUNT(*) as cnt,
  GROUP_CONCAT(CONCAT(id, ':', civilId, ':', COALESCE(name, 'NULL')) SEPARATOR ' | ') as patients
FROM patients
GROUP BY normCid
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
ORDER BY cnt DESC
LIMIT 30;
